{"tid":2267493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真的是腰束奶澎！雞排妹新造型曝光⋯辣曬「神級碗公奶」","createTime":"2020-11-02T06:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T09:18:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfec855695861787dbeacd3b5eecd28e72f14b7","tid":2267493,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"女星雞排妹（鄭家純）擁有天使臉蛋、魔鬼身材，個性直率的她話題尺度超大，近來更主持網路深夜節目，大談兩性議題，受到許多粉絲喜愛。近日她就在社群平台曬出新造型，只見她化身成美豔「貓妖」一身古代妃子裝更擠出渾圓碗公奶。<br />\n<br />\n收到遊戲代言，雞排妹上月31日在IG寫下「今天萬聖節🎃阿純扮成商戰RPG遊戲活動期間限定紅顏角色『靈夜貓妖』」超精緻的妝容搭配大紅色系的口紅，襯托出雞排妹雪白的肌膚。另外幾張則是工作人員在一旁幫忙穿衣的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n然而其中最大亮點莫過於雞排妹的性感妃子裝，半截式的設計讓上圍呼之欲出，且在腰部還用力拉出小蠻腰，完整還原「腰束奶澎」4個字。有趣的是，在最後幾張照片還出現《戲說台灣》的主題曲配樂，粉絲看完秒破功喊「戲說台灣我直接笑噴XDD」"},{"pid":"23befafea175a7414ab538814fc3c7f0e44b84f3","tid":2267493,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2856887-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2856887-PH.jpg&h=63dde7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼雞排妹接下遊戲代言，換上性感服裝。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2856886-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2856886-PH.jpg&h=a253386e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"831f8b64bad6d4b802317f0e1870ead1d39d8f8f","tid":2267493,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f389724aeeb67851bb5f05b84bc528d74e990ef4","tid":2267493,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"831f8b64bad6d4b802317f0e1870ead1d39d8f8f","tid":2267493,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi